com.google.template.soy.soytree

Class TemplateRegistry.DelegateTemplateDivision

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.template.soy.soytree.TemplateRegistry.DelegateTemplateDivision
  • Enclosing class:
    TemplateRegistry

    public static final class TemplateRegistry.DelegateTemplateDivision
extends Object
    Represents a set of delegate templates with the same key (name and variant) and same priority.

    Note: Per delegate rules, at most one of the templates in each division may be active at render time.

    Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).
